data.description: Motivated Seller! Price improvement! Updates include a newer roof, brand new AC, updated electrial, replumbed, stainless steel appliances, and refinished wood flooring throughout. This home is perfect for those seeking a comfortable and cozy place to call home. With 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms and an extra space that could be a 4th bedroom or flex space. As you walk in you are greeted with an updated kitchen, dining room perfect for entertaining and  and plenty of storage space. Relax outside on your paver patio and enjoy a nice evening by the fire pit in your fully fenced backyard.  Ask about the assumable 5.65% mortgage & schedule your showing today!
